President Cyril Ramaphosa has described the late former President Nelson Mandela as the greatest leader of our time. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa has described the late former president Nelson Mandela as the greatest leader of our time. July 18 marks International Mandela Day, and the world is paying homage to the late statesman for his fight against apartheid. WATCH: 18th Nelson Mandela Annual Lecture Ramaphosa says Mandela's legacy can teach the world valuable lessons against injustice.